verbose_text: LXRs upregulate ABC transporters including ABCA1, ABCG1, ABCG4, ABCG5 and ABCG8 that shuttle intracellular cholesterol for the efflux out of cells, and several apolipoproteins including apo AI and E. ABCA1 is a key playmaker in cholesterol efflux, and a major determinant of plasma HDL level [XREF_BIBR].
